readable_query: SELECT Spectroscopic_objects.object_id, Spectroscopic_objects.spectroscopic_class, Spectroscopic_objects.spectroscopic_subclass FROM specobj AS Spectroscopic_objects JOIN photoobj AS photoobj ON Spectroscopic_objects.best_object_id = photoobj.object_id JOIN photo_type AS photometrically_observed ON photoobj.object_type_classification = photometrically_observed.value WHERE Spectroscopic_objects.spectroscopic_subclass like "%AGN%" and Spectroscopic_objects.spectroscopic_class = "GALAXY" and photometrically_observed.name = "GALAXY"
